snippet: The death toll in the partial collapse of a four-story apartment building in the Paris suburb of Rosny-sous-Bois rose to eight on Monday after emergency crews pulled the bodies of a man and a woman from the rubble.
lead_paragraph: The death toll in the partial collapse of a four-story apartment building in the Paris suburb of Rosny-sous-Bois rose to eight on Monday after emergency crews pulled the bodies of a man and a woman from the rubble.

headline.main: France: Death Toll Rises to 8 After Building Collapse
